  "description": [
    "2 E DI T O R 1 A 1 5 A test of civil rights We wish that we could welcome without reservations the establishment by Corporation Counsel Barnet Hodes of a Civil Rights Unit of the city Unfortunately however the events of the last week tend to mar the picture The same Mr Hodes is known to be responsible for the fact that Claude Lightfoot an independent candidate for State Senator in the sth District a Negro and a Com munist may be barred from the ballot Now this raises the question of whether Mr Hodes sees the full picture of the violation of civil rights in tfiis city or whether his vision is distorted by the fact that the Democratic Party expects him to deliver his sth Ward which is part of the sth District Its a case where liberalism and genuine champion ship of civil rights come in conflict with the dictates of the higherups of the party machine Certainly the 10600 Negro and white citizens of the sth District who signed his petitions are not going to ac cept any decision that rules Claude Lightfoot off the ballot It is all very well to talk about"
  ],
